              target="_blank"
              >heatwave in Greece</a
            >
            is affecting the detainees, and aid boxes have remained closed as
            officials fear provoking a fight. Officials arrest the asylum
            seekers from Sudan and other African countries, not giving them time
            to explain their story.
          </p>
