            <strong
              >Summary: Russian engagement with Africa provides the Kremlin with
              an offensive frontline, but the West is warned.</strong
            >
          </p>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5">
            <strong>The what:</strong> Russia‚Äôs
            <a
              style="
                text-decoration: none;
                border-bottom: 2px solid #06266d;
                color: black;
              "
              href="https://link.geopoliticalsummary.com/gs-31-jul-25-analysis-h1-8-engagement-with-the-african-continent"
